    "Per-variable non-null counts by year, focused on the post-2019 window. Use this to decide whether to keep the extended panel unbalanced (default), drop year-variable combinations with thin coverage, or upgrade specific sources (e.g. PWT 11.0 -> 11.1 for HCI).\n"
